0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去月經個留日講座 睇晒咁多間資料先再問都未遲啦 個個人要求都唔同 叫人點答你</blockquote><br />\n黎緊都會去 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我下年4月都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905a9c81545f710f9cdf4307224c1d99bea938dd","tid":288682,"uid":12083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去月經個留日講座 睇晒咁多間資料先再問都未遲啦 個個人要求都唔同 叫人點答你</blockquote><br />\n黎緊都會去 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我下年4月都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打會去邊? 係咪都係白紙去?"},{"pid":"39de600bca7c2f9e46a1a8392d257c69ee51018d","tid":288682,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去月經個留日講座 睇晒咁多間資料先再問都未遲啦 個個人要求都唔同 叫人點答你</blockquote><br />\n黎緊都會去 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我下年4月都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打會去邊? 係咪都係白紙去?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n半白紙啦 7月2試考N4 我睇左幾個月教學片 都識少少既 我未決定 不過都係東京同大阪二選一"},{"pid":"07a8053e22d9a45f6917f1e5c6a713ce847a95c9","tid":288682,"uid":68935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"我今年28歲，做左幾年野，大學沒exchange,，想趁30前留下學，想下年去<br />\n有沒知平均一個月租地方住，洗費幾錢？"},{"pid":"9a56f75377b48641a5af2f46bb84c2652d019a52","tid":288682,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今年28歲，做左幾年野，大學沒exchange,，想趁30前留下學，想下年去<br />\n有沒知平均一個月租地方住，洗費幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n我都想下年去 你想去咩地方先？<br />\n東京住唔同區都唔同價"},{"pid":"2863ac2b578940f60056fc8f03ff93306bc79e88","tid":288682,"uid":2012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今年28歲，做左幾年野，大學沒exchange,，想趁30前留下學，想下年去<br />\n有沒知平均一個月租地方住，洗費幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n住share house啦 除非有本地人肯幫你做保證人 <br />\n保證人公司貴 我果時住就六萬幾yen一個月 自己一間房 share 廁所 <br />\n洗費就睇人啦 我平時唔會自己煮飯 我就萬二左右一個月全包(屋租水電 車費 食)<br />\n<br />\n讀左四年"},{"pid":"358187375e7187e0d289ba365109e7fa84847f1d","tid":288682,"uid":61497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今年28歲，做左幾年野，大學沒exchange,，想趁30前留下學，想下年去<br />\n有沒知平均一個月租地方住，洗費幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n各大地產都有啲外國人，免保証人既屋可以租<br />\n價錢就睇離車站距離/新舊/地區<br />\n仲有禮金同中介費等等雜費，當然有啲係全免，不過個租金又會貴返啲<br />\n慢慢睇下再決定<br />\n仲有共益費 ，水電煤， 一個人既正常預多一萬到"},{"pid":"182af246473d050a7c975a8530b6dea95df32692","tid":288682,"uid":91724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"想問下 如果dse雞讀書麻麻 想去日本讀 讀完語言學校  <br />\n讀大學定短大定專門學校好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19108146419690f1b5073cfdc1a03eeacb502bb3","tid":288682,"uid":6513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下 如果dse雞讀書麻麻 想去日本讀 讀完語言學校  <br />\n讀大學定短大定專門學校好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你想讀咩相關<br />\nEg econ bba 理工呢啲就入U<br />\n其他比較重技巧嘅 animation 音樂 廚藝呢啲就短大/専門"},{"pid":"6d00db7894d8f570cff220ede5d31b743c133619","tid":288682,"uid":99175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:36:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下 如果dse雞讀書麻麻 想去日本讀 讀完語言學校  <br />\n讀大學定短大定專門學校好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你想讀咩相關<br />\nEg econ bba 理工呢啲就入U<br />\n其他比較重技巧嘅 animation 音樂 廚藝呢啲就短大/専門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廚藝都有得讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9286f58a0576c6beda54c52664d301d17f758a","tid":288682,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:40:59.000Z","msg":"日本大學用英文教書？"},{"pid":"49786046f01f900be47a872334a3f63773900538","tid":288682,"uid":6513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T19:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下 如果dse雞讀書麻麻 想去日本讀 讀完語言學校  <br />\n讀大學定短大定專門學校好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你想讀咩相關<br />\nEg econ bba 理工呢啲就入U<br />\n其他比較重技巧嘅 animation 音樂 廚藝呢啲就短大/専門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廚藝都有得讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本專門學校好多花款<br />\n我語言學校同班嘅入Design 又有，製菓又有，汽車又有"},{"pid":"2ffcd9e5728ef171b29e8305d218af1543f1b531","tid":288682,"uid":91724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T10:54:46.000Z","msg":"想問下係日本升學 大多數國立定私立？ 唔知國立難唔難考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a3bffa1dc717396e0e22c5e420e0eeac42e8e6","tid":288682,"uid":57608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"下年想試下報東大嘅master<br />\n好想去日本讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}